                    <span>I read this book immediately following Jon Lee Anderson's "Che Guevara: A Revolutionary Life"...I didn't think I would be as impressed, but I was.  I recommend both books for anyone who wants to get a real picture of Che...I would suggest starting with Anderson's and following with this one, as I did.  
<br />
<br />Well written, informative, well researched, unbiased.  Highly recommended.</span>
                  
