                    <span>I like this book a lot.  The author obviously did a lot of research and has passion about the subject.  I've always been fascinated by the life of Che and what he represented.  I also enjoy reading biographies.  However, the extensive use of footnotes and the long chapters did make the reading tiresome sometimes.  </span>
                  
              
